@startuml
[*] --> PowerOnCheck
PowerOnCheck --> [*]
PowerOnCheck --> StartupError : problem detected
PowerOnCheck --> ReadyToUse : everything fine

ReadyToUse --> Reset : reset system
ReadyToUse --> Activate : activate system
ReadyToUse --> TurnOff : turn off system
Activate --> Monitoring : start monitoring
Monitoring --> AlarmActive : sensor triggered
AlarmActive --> [*] : alarm and send alerts
AlarmActive --> Monitoring : false alarm or time ends

ReadyToUse --> [*] : enter password
@enduml
